page.title: 09Specific Occupations, Woking
page.content: I live in Laurel Crescent,Woodham Lane and am a Manager with Chase Manhatten Bank which is the third largest American bank. Their office in London has about 1200 employees. I am involved in providing financial services to individuals but mostly to companies, some of which are in the Middle East. I am a State Registered Nurse working part-time at St.Peter's Hospital in Chertsey. I do Night Duty one or two nights per week, usually on a different ward each night with patients of all ages and with many different illnesses. My shift starts at 8.55pm and finishes at 7.30am. I am a Secretary to an Insurance Broker in Woking Town Centre, chiefly helping to find money for people to buy houses. Six people work in the office from 8.30am to 4.45pm.
